flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 69: Observability Signal Topology (Metrics, Logs, Traces, Errors)

  Services[Runtime services\nweb/api/worker/data]

  Metrics[Prometheus]
  Logs[Loki]
  OTel[OpenTelemetry Collector]
  Traces[Tempo]
  Errors[Sentry]

  Dash[Grafana dashboards]
  Alerts[Alert routing and on-call notifications]
  SinkIssue{Any telemetry sink unavailable?}
  Buffer[Buffer degraded telemetry and preserve critical signals]
  Replay[Replay buffered telemetry after sink recovery]

  Services -->|metrics| Metrics
  Services -->|logs| Logs
  Services -->|traces| OTel --> Traces
  Services -->|errors| Errors

  Metrics --> Dash
  Logs --> Dash
  Traces --> Dash
  Errors --> Dash

  Dash --> Alerts

  Metrics --> SinkIssue
  Logs --> SinkIssue
  Traces --> SinkIssue
  Errors --> SinkIssue
  SinkIssue -- Yes --> Buffer
  Buffer --> Replay --> Dash
  SinkIssue -- No --> Dash
